{"books":[{"id":"maoquanji1","name":"毛泽东全集第1卷","internal":false,"type":"pdf","official":false,"author":"张迪杰","files":["https://raw.githubusercontent.com/banned-historical-archives/banned-historical-archives8/main/maoquanji1.pdf"],"article":{"title":"五言诗·玉潭即景联句","alias":"","parts":[{"type":"paragraph","text":"五言诗·玉潭即景\"联句"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"（1917年）云封狮固楼，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"桥锁玉潭舟。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"[1]玉潭，即玉潭河，在湖南宁乡城郊。即景，眼前景物，后因称以眼前景物为题材的诗为即景诗。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"[2]云封，指云气遮蔽。狮固，即狮固山，是宁乡县东北3里的一座小山。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"[3]桥，指宁乡县城郊玉潭河上的一座小桥。桥锁玉潭舟，意思是说，玉潭河中，许多船停泊在桥边，像是被桥锁住一样。"}],"authors":["毛泽东"],"dates":[{"year":1917}],"is_range_date":false,"comments":[],"comment_pivots":[],"description":"","page_start":300,"page_end":300},"tags":[{"name":"毛泽东","type":"人物"},{"type":"文稿类型","name":"文章"}]}]}